OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1774548358
OL,3,C'44% rise in fuel costs over the last
OL,4,Ctwo weeks alone' says Derry bus company
OL,6,FA Londonderry bus company has told UTV
OL,7,Fthat its costs have soared since the
OL,8,Fbeginning of the war in the Middle
OL,9,FEast.
OL,11,FIt follows the ongoing uncertainty
OL,12,Faround rising fuel prices, which has
OL,13,Fled to calls for targeted support, to
OL,14,Fhelp the industry.
OL,16,FOn Tuesday, the Irish government
OL,17,Fannounced cuts on petrol and diesel
OL,18,Fprices up until at least May.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
