OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1774548358
OL,3,C'44% rise in fuel costs over the last
OL,4,Ctwo weeks alone' says Derry bus company
OL,6,FWhile petrol remains more expensive,
OL,7,Fdiesel is generally on par, if not a
OL,8,Flittle bit cheaper, than many places
OL,9,Fin Northern Ireland.
OL,11,FChris Arthur's family own a bus
OL,12,Fcompany in Limavady, where volatility
OL,13,Fat the pumps has hit hard.
OL,15,FMr Arthur said: "We're filling about
OL,16,F2,000 to 3,000 litres a week,
OL,17,Fdepending on what we're doing.
OL,19,F"We're looking at a 44% rise in fuel
OL,20,F(costs) over the last two weeks alone."
OL,26,@|D@Apm|D@Gpn
