OL,3,C'44% rise in fuel costs over the last
OL,4,Ctwo weeks alone' says Derry bus company
OL,6,FAs one of the most prominent transport
OL,7,Fcompanies in the north west, they have
OL,8,Fcontracts with the Education Authority
OL,9,Fto bring children to and from school.
OL,11,FChris said the transport sector in
OL,12,FNorthern Ireland needs help.
OL,14,F"I think that if it keeps continuing
OL,15,Fgoing the way that it's going, I think
OL,16,Fthat you're going to be seeing a lot
OL,17,Fof the home-to-school transport
OL,18,Faffected.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
