CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1774548358
OL,3,C'44% rise in fuel costs over the last
OL,4,Ctwo weeks alone' says Derry bus company
OL,6,F"You may see prices increasing. I'm
OL,7,Fpricing runs for June, and I'm nearly
OL,8,Fembarrassed giving them a price.
OL,10,F"I'm telling customers that we are
OL,11,Fgoing to have to keep it under review,
OL,12,Fand if the fuel comes down, we'll
OL,13,Fbring the price back down.
OL,15,FUTV has asked the Education Minister
OL,16,Fif there are any plans to introduce
OL,17,Fsupport for bus companies transporting
OL,18,Fschool children.
OL,20,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,21,FITVX
